<div class= "mpep belowNavBar">
  <p class= "midday"><%= dgettext "np", "Communion of the Sick"%></p>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", "The Minister begins"%></p>
  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ. 
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class= "rubric_black"><%= dgettext "sick", "Philippians 1:2"%></p>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", "The Minister continues"%></p>
  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Almighty God, to you all hearts are open, all desires known, and from you 
    no secrets are hid: Cleanse the thoughts of our hearts by the inspiration 
    of your Holy Spirit, that we may perfectly love you, and worthily magnify 
    your holy Name; through Christ our Lord.
    """%>
    <span class="italic"><%= dgettext "sick", "Amen." %></span>
  </p>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", "A Psalm may be prayed. Psalms"%>
    <button class="psalm-button" data-psalm="23">23</button>, 
    <button class="psalm-button" data-psalm="62">62</button>, 
    <button class="psalm-button" data-psalm="103">103</button>
    <%= dgettext "sick", "and" %>
    <button class="psalm-button" data-psalm="145">145</button>
    <%= dgettext "sick", "are particularly appropriate. "%>
  </p>
  <div id="sick-communion-psalm"></div>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    One of the following Gospel lessons is read, or the readings appropriate to the day
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    For God so loved the world, that he gave his only Son, that whoever believes in 
    him should not perish but have eternal life.
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class="rubric_black"><%= dgettext "sick", "John 3:16"%></p>
  <br>
  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Jesus said, “I am the living bread that came down from heaven. If anyone 
    eats of this bread, he will live forever. And the bread that I will give 
    for the life of the world is my flesh.” For my flesh is true food, and my 
    blood is true drink. Whoever feeds on my flesh and drinks my blood abides 
    in me, and I in him. 
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class="rubric_black"><%= dgettext "sick", "John 6:51, 55-56"%></p>

  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Reflection on the lessons may follow.
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    The minister may say the confession and the sick person joins in as able.
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "Most merciful God,"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "we confess that we have sinned against you"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "in thought, word and deed,"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "by what we have done, and by what we have left undone."%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "We have not loved you with our whole heart;"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "we have not loved our neighbors as ourselves."%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "We are truly sorry and we humbly repent."%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "For the sake of your Son Jesus Christ,"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "have mercy on us and forgive us;"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "that we may delight in your will, and walk in your ways,"%></p>
  <p class= "alt_confession pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "to the glory of your Name. Amen."%></p>
    
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    A Priest, if present, says
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Almighty God, our heavenly Father, who in his great mercy has promised forgiveness 
    of sins to all those who sincerely repent and with true faith turn to him, have 
    mercy upon you, pardon and deliver you from all your sins, confirm and strengthen 
    you in all goodness, and bring you to everlasting life;
    through Jesus Christ our Lord. 
    """%>
    <span class="italic"><%= dgettext "sick", "Amen." %></span>
  </p>
    
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    A Deacon or lay person prays
    """%>
  </p>
  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Grant your faithful people, merciful Lord, pardon and peace; that we may 
    be cleansed from all our sins, and serve you with a quiet mind; through 
    Jesus Christ our Lord.
    """%>
    <span class="italic"><%= dgettext "sick", "Amen." %></span>
  </p>
  <br>

  <p class="office">
    <span class="versical-speaker"><%= dgettext "sick", "Minister"%></span>
    <span class="versical-speaker-says"><%= dgettext "sick", "The peace of the Lord be always with you."%></span>
  </p>
  <p class="office">
    <span class="versical-speaker"><%= dgettext "sick", "People"%></span>
    <span class="versical-speaker-says"><%= dgettext "sick", "And with your spirit. "%></span>
  </p>
  <p class="office">
    <span class="versical-speaker"><%= dgettext "sick", "Minister"%></span>
    <span class="versical-speaker-says"><%= dgettext "sick", "Let us pray."%></span>
  </p>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Minister and People
    """%>
  </p>
  <%= render "_lords_prayer_trad.html" %>
  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    Then may be said
    """%>
  </p>
  <%= render "_agnus_dei.html" %>

  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    The minister may say
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    The body of our Lord Jesus Christ, which was given for you, 
    preserve your body and soul to everlasting life. 
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class="office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    The blood of our Lord Jesus Christ, which was shed for you, 
    preserve your body and soul to everlasting life.
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    After Communion, the minister says
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "Almighty and ever-living God,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "we thank you for feeding us, in these holy mysteries,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "with the spiritual food of the most precious Body and Blood"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "of your Son our Savior Jesus Christ;"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "and for assuring us, through this Sacrament, of your favor and goodness towards us;"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "and that we are true members of the mystical body of your Son,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "the blessed company of all faithful people;"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "and are also heirs, through hope, of your everlasting kingdom."%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "And we humbly ask you, heavenly Father,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "to assist us with your grace,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "that we may continue in that holy fellowship,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "and do all such good works as you have prepared for us to walk in;"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "through Jesus Christ our Lord,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "to whom with you and the Holy Spirit,"%></p>
  <p class= "pb_vs"><%= dgettext "sick", "be all honor and glory, now and forever. Amen."%></p>

  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    A Priest gives this blessing
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class= "office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    The peace of God which passes all understanding keep your hearts and minds in the 
    knowledge and love of God, and of his Son Jesus Christ our Lord; and the blessing 
    of God Almighty, the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit, be among you, and remain 
    with you always. 
    """%>
    <span class="italic"><%= dgettext "sick", "Amen." %></span>    
  </p>

  <p class="rubric-office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    A Deacon or lay person says the following
    """%>
  </p>

  <p class= "office"><%= dgettext "sick", """
    The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ, and the love of God, and the fellowship of the 
    Holy Spirit, be with us all evermore.  
    """%>
    <span class="italic"><%= dgettext "sick", "Amen." %></span>
  </p>
  <p class="rubric_black"><%= dgettext "sick", "2 Corinthians 13:14"%></p>
  <br>

  <p class="office">
    <span class="versical-speaker"><%= dgettext "sick", "Minister"%></span>
    <span class="versical-speaker-says"><%= dgettext "sick", "Let us bless the Lord."%></span>
  </p>
  <p class="office">
    <span class="versical-speaker"><%= dgettext "sick", "People"%></span>
    <span class="versical-speaker-says"><%= dgettext "sick", "Thanks be to God."%></span>
  </p>


</div>